
Three examples of defined MPI data types are given:

- MPI_Type_Vector (userdefined_types1) 
- MPI_Type_Indexed (userdefined_types2) 
- MPI_Type_Create_Subarray (userdefined_types3)

By typing make all three examples will be compiled. 
Run the code executables with 2 MPI-tasks

mpirun -np 2 ....

Is the code doing the correct communication?

-1-

  Change userdefined_types1 the dimension to 8 and sent only the odd rows to the other MPI-tasks

-2-

In userdefined_types3 change code to wite subarray of 2x2 in top left corner or array

